NON-AFFILIATION / FAN-WORK NOTICE

This project is an unofficial, non-profit fan recreation of the puzzle game
EDGE, originally created by Mobigame SARL and published on various platforms
by Mobigame and Two Tribes. The EDGE name, game design, and all associated
trademarks and copyrights belong to their respective owners. This project is
not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Mobigame or Two Tribes, and
it is not sold or monetized in any form. It exists purely as a programming
exercise and a tribute. If you enjoy it, please support the original:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/38740/EDGE/
